    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained over the years. You\u2019ll find it runs beautifully and still looks great parked in the driveway! It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a reliable, comfy daily driver that\u2019s ready to hit the road right away. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
