    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit boasts precise throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Key enthusiast maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive double VANOS overhaul. The suspension utilizes a factory-spec MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, maintaining excellent lateral grip through the M-variable limited-slip differential. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system refresh. A driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
