    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is a stunning example of refined luxury and Japanese engineering. The Atomic Silver exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye might spot a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with regular highway commuting. Step inside to a cabin wrapped in Parchment leather; the seats remain supportive and plush, with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s bolster and no tears or stains. All electronics, from the premium surround-sound system to the heated and ventilated seats, function perfectly. Under the hood, the V6 engine purrs with the same smoothness it had on day one, backed by a comprehensive service history. It rides on a set of Michelin tires with plenty of tread remaining, ensuring a quiet and stable journey. This vehicle has been smoke-free, pet-free, and garage-kept, offering a premium driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
