      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been super reliable and runs like a dream! The interior is nice and clean, and it's been well-loved and looked after. It\u2019s the perfect ride for someone who wants a solid, dependable car without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
